{
  "texts": [
    "However, when adopting the class-balanced focal loss instead of the cross-entropy loss, the model trained with AuSTR solely achieved comparable results to that augmented model, indicating that AuSTR solely, despite the limited size, can be sufficient for detecting the stance of authorities.",
    "Finally, out of our extensive failure analysis, we recommend further work on tweet preprocessing to consider context expansion, and exploring other stance models that can detect the implicit stance and take the authorities writing style into consideration.",
    "Since our study focused on Arabic data, examining the task in other languages is clearly a potential path for future work.",
    "https:// github.",
    "com/ Fatima-Haoua ri/ AuSTR"
  ]
}